{"tha-ap226:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap226:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap226:0.3":"Arakkhadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap226:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap226:1.2":"vedi karapita maya; ","tha-ap226:1.3":"Arakkho ca maya dinno, ","tha-ap226:1.4":"sugatassa mahesino. ","tha-ap226:2.1":"Tena kammavisesena, ","tha-ap226:2.2":"na passim bhayabheravam; ","tha-ap226:2.3":"Kuhinci upapannassa, ","tha-ap226:2.4":"taso mayham na vijjati. ","tha-ap226:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap226:3.2":"yam vedim karayim pure; ","tha-ap226:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap226:3.4":"vedikaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap226:4.1":"Ito chatthamhi kappamhi, ","tha-ap226:4.2":"apassenasanamako; ","tha-ap226:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap226:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap226:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap226:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap226:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap226:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma arakkhadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap226:7.1":"Arakkhadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}